text: Kyle James Kozub Mooney (born September 4, 1984) is an American comedian, actor, and writer. He has been a cast member of Saturday Night Live from 2013 until 2022. His man-on-the-street interviews have been featured on Jimmy Kimmel Live! and Sports Show with Norm Macdonald. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from San Diego Category:Comedians from San Diego Category:Writers from California
